">    </span><span class=\"n\">funext</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">show</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">add_comm</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TestClass</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>also works.</p>",
